{"tid":1024067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡呆母說「去隔壁找兒子」傻走643公里　8個月後在另一個國家找到她","createTime":"2019-02-16T09:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T10:27:30.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"76c3796708232cc4a1b35fdee257922dfdf22ffe","tid":1024067,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"文／紅豆Q粉粿<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/3899565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2F3899565.jpg&h=7bb4542a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家中若有罹患失智症的老父母，子女們一定要多留心才是呀！<br />\n泰國近期有一件失蹤案引起熱議，一位患有失智症的患者，竟徒步走了643公里遠，被發現時，已身在另一個國家！<br />\n事情是這樣的，名為Kaeomanee的七旬老婦，她患有嚴重的失智症，不僅說話方式像孩子，智力和記憶力也都退化，一旦出門便很容易迷失方向，找不到回家的路。有一天，Kaeomanee看女兒Suchada在忙，匆匆忙忙地想出門，出門前她回頭說了一句，「兒子就在隔壁，我去找他！」接著便踏出家門。<br />\n一時大意的Suchada沒有馬上攔住母親，直到當晚才發現母親走失了，一家人焦急地到處找了好幾天、好幾個月，都沒有下文，他們甚至已經做好心理準備，心想Kaeomanee可能遭逢不幸&hellip;<br />\n但，奇蹟發生了！過了八個月後，有泰國人到大陸昆明遊玩，看到Kaeomanee，一眼就認出來她是失蹤者，趕緊通報泰國當局，聽到Kaeomanee還活著的消息，Suchada和其他家人都感到又驚又喜，直接飛到泰國去接回Kaeomanee。<br />\nSuchada事後說，這一定是奇蹟！但他們萬萬沒想到，事隔八個多月，母親竟然靠著徒步行走，一路走了643公里，從泰國走到大陸去了！這實在很不可思議！<br />\n然而，最幸運的還是，Kaeomanee終於和家人團聚了呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/3899567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2F3899567.jpg&h=39915357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F41740&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=292a0895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41740</a>"},{"pid":"f44e0fd795fba1d9a320ad3cc6fd824ec354aa33","tid":1024067,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466fd26804825e353a15ac860c8988d78b786baa","tid":1024067,"uid":20058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"但係其實泰國同支那根本冇接壤<br />\n即係佢根本過咗兩個國家嘅邊境先去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4224d4d78ffce13d8f2ce40b7a1408042213a2c5","tid":1024067,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"大陸搵得番又會無事<br />\n係咪山寨版嚟?"},{"pid":"af7168f51e1fa0171c4dbf582d2b6b8df67eb5d8","tid":1024067,"uid":38391,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"有泰國人到大陸昆明遊玩，看到Kaeomanee，一眼就認出來她是失蹤者，趕緊通報泰國當局，聽到Kaeomanee還活著的消息，Suchada和其他家人都感到又驚又喜，<span style=\"color: red;\">直接飛到泰國</span>去接回Kaeomanee。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ef92b6fb94a2932d5e4a23614060de21414a1d","tid":1024067,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"8個月 佢年衫幾乾淨"},{"pid":"3eea70a7265ca06b4065a6948e2a5b1347edc7f9","tid":1024067,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"8個月點生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b12549eade346ff73021c77b29f494d72fa8ea9","tid":1024067,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"佢到底食咩為生係哩8個月入面"},{"pid":"ff00c2e850aafdc2df7e8ed078cd44cdfbfb6440","tid":1024067,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"食草？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102b2afe5980e7341cf65078546489108d17c432","tid":1024067,"uid":92340,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:2